parameters.name: offset
parameters.description: The number of results to skip from the beginning of the available set

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: The maximum number of results to read from the available set

parameters.name: sort
parameters.description: A specification of one or more fields to sort results by. Of format `<field> [asc | desc]`. Sortable Fields: [timestamp]

parameters.name: filter
parameters.description: A specification of properties to <<filtering,filter>> results by. Of format `<filterKey>:<filterValue>`. Supported Filters: [journalObjectType, journalObjectNames, journalTriggerNames, journalDate, journalAction]
